rows.label: tlk70000021_02_msg0001
rows.name:
This business's got some people
disheartened and some afeared...

rows.label: tlk70000021_02_msg0002
rows.name: Not me. It fires me up, is what it does.

rows.label: tlk70000021_02_msg0003
rows.name:
What's broke we'll fix! What's needed
we'll make! We can build all sorts of
things for Iira and our people.

rows.label: tlk70000021_02_msg0004
rows.name:
I haven't got time to feel sad! I'm going
to support Iira with my work.
I've set my heart and mind on it!
